    dc:description "FIGURES 86 – 88. Alaptus spp. ♀ (NMID). 86, section of A. H. Haliday’s drawer of Mymaridae with lectotype of A. fusculus; 87, slide envelope of A. minimus lectotype; 88, slide of A. minimus lectotype." ;
